data.description: Cute St. Augustine Shores home on a quiet street! Concrete block construction. Sunroom leads to the patio where you can relax & enjoy the outdoors & views of the green space in the back. Large, elevated lot with conservation area to the rear & right of the property, giving the large backyard & patio area a private, park-like setting. Room for children to play and a great space for gardening. Upgrades include Barron's water filtration system (retail $5995) and a wired security system that you can operate from your app, includes security panel, 2 cameras & door entry. Windows/storm panels 2006, new electrical panel 2019, HVAC 2015, plumbing updates to remove non-PVC sections 2023, water heater 2022. The St. Augustine Shores offers 30 miles of walking trails, Intracoastal fishing from community pier, pool, community center & clubhouse. Close to Publix, hospital, shopping, restaurants, 15 min to beach, historic downtown & more! Would make a great starter home or investment property! Great tenants in place with lease thru Mar 31, 2024.
